Sentencas: This paper studies the effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in bonded compliant seal of solid oxide fuel cell by finite element method.
Titulo: Effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in the bonded compliant seal of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A strain based creep damage model is used, and its feasibility to predict the creep damage behavior of the materials is verified firstly by the experimental data.
Titulo: Effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in the bonded compliant seal of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results show that the failure locates at the foil and the location varies with the temperature increasing.
Titulo: Effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in the bonded compliant seal of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: When the temperature is lower than 600 degrees C, there is nearly no crack occurs.
Titulo: Effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in the bonded compliant seal of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: When the temperature is 600 degrees C, the creep crack belongs to internal crack and the length is about 2.5 mm.
Titulo: Effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in the bonded compliant seal of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: While the temperature is 650 degrees C or higher, the crack locates at the foil surface and the length is larger than 25 mm at an operation time of 50,000 h.
Titulo: Effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in the bonded compliant seal of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Compared to the size of the whole structure, an internal crack of 2.5 mm is small and the gas leakage will not happen.
Titulo: Effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in the bonded compliant seal of planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Therefore, it can satisfy the requirement of safe operation for more than 40,000 h. Thus, it recommends that the operating temperature should not be higher than 600 degrees C on the condition of insuring the power performance and operation cost of the SOFC.
Titulo: Effect of operating temperature on creep and damage in the bonded compliant seal of planar solid oxide fuel cell
